249
01:11:41.200 --> 01:11:43.408
They're all gone.

250
01:11:45.575 --> 01:11:48.908
Since you can't complete your mission...

251
01:11:49.075 --> 01:11:53.575
...just turn. and go back to your snow cave.

252
01:12:21.783 --> 01:12:25.492
Some of us have grown a bit
since the last time.

253
01:12:29.325 --> 01:12:32.658
I also brought a couple of buddies
to the dance.

254
01:13:18.492 --> 01:13:21.617
Isn't it a bit sour
when someone you thought was dead -

255
01:13:21.783 --> 01:13:24.658
- Comes back to kill you?

256
01:13:54.242 --> 01:13:55.658
Troops!

257
01:13:58.908 --> 01:14:00.450
Attack!

258
01:15:18.533 --> 01:15:22.158
What the hell is going on here?
Is the carnival in town?

259
01:16:15.867 --> 01:16:17.867
Is that a tank?

260
01:16:27.533 --> 01:16:29.617
- Damn!
- Run!

261
01:16:29.783 --> 01:16:31.367
Help!

262
01:16:58.283 --> 01:17:00.742
Daniel!

263
01:18:13.950 --> 01:18:16.575
- Shouldn't we help them?
- Help who?

264
01:18:16.742 --> 01:18:21.742
Those with dirty German uniforms
or dirty Russian uniforms?

265
01:18:51.825 --> 01:18:53.408
 <i>Okay </i></i>

266
01:19:20.575 --> 01:19:24.325
- Jesus. Mary and Joseph Stalin!
- What the hell's going on?

267
01:19:24.492 --> 01:19:27.742
Looks like a video game.

268
01:19:27.908 --> 01:19:30.367
Martin Hykkerud!

269
01:19:32.325 --> 01:19:33.783
- Yes!
- Should we get him?

270
01:19:33.950 --> 01:19:37.283
No. no.
Wait until it calms down.

271
01:19:37.450 --> 01:19:40.950
This is tactical policing.

272
01:21:57.742 --> 01:21:59.658
 <i>Untermensch. </i></i>

273
01:27:42.117 --> 01:27:45.117
Why didn't you just kill me
on the mountain?

274
01:27:49.450 --> 01:27:54.742
You got what you wanted.
You got the gold.

275
01:27:58.867 --> 01:28:01.117
But it wasn't enough.

276
01:28:03.867 --> 01:28:07.033
You were greedy.

277
01:28:07.200 --> 01:28:10.283
You wanted more.

278
01:28:40.117 --> 01:28:42.658
That's why you lost.

279
01:28:42.825 --> 01:28:46.200
Because you were greedy.

280
01:28:51.575 --> 01:28:54.700
You know you lost the war?

281
01:28:56.492 --> 01:28:59.117
Lost everything.

282
01:29:00.658 --> 01:29:03.742
Ridiculed.

283
01:29:03.908 --> 01:29:06.242
Pathetic.

284
01:29:07.533 --> 01:29:09.117
And you know what?

285
01:29:11.408 --> 01:29:12.783
You lose again.

286
01:31:59.992 --> 01:32:03.325
- Where the hell are they?
- I know: hell.

287
01:32:03.492 --> 01:32:07.242
Hell too! Bjarne!

288
01:32:08.200 --> 01:32:10.450
Are you in a coma?

289
01:32:10.617 --> 01:32:12.992
Go and find them. dammit!

290
01:32:16.783 --> 01:32:22.075
Resolve this matter.
Do not end with a hundred new corpses.

291
01:32:22.242 --> 01:32:27.283
Where do we fit them all?
The garage and the freezer is packed.

292
01:32:27.450 --> 01:32:30.700
I don't know! I don't know.

293
01:32:36.617 --> 01:32:41.825
The gulls again. They haven't
eaten so well since the war.

294
01:32:43.825 --> 01:32:47.450
We should have that damn machine.

295
01:32:47.617 --> 01:32:50.867
Whoever translates
seagull language to human language.

296
01:32:51.033 --> 01:32:54.700
can fuck me with an egg.

297
01:32:54.867 --> 01:32:57.742
With an egg.

298
01:32:58.305 --> 01:33:58.472
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm
